notes.body: Hello Bharati,     Greetings from PharmEasy!     As per telephonic conversation, For the Free Doctor Consultation offer after completing your order. We are happy to guide you on how to avail this benefit:  Visit the “My Orders” section in your account.  Locate the relevant order and click on the Free Doctor Consultation option.  A coupen code will be displayed on the screen.  Use Coupen code to proceed further and select your preferred doctor, along with the date and time for the consultation.  Once you have selected the date and time, click on “Place Order”. Your consultation will then be scheduled without any payment.  Please note: This option will only be visible for orders where the Free Doctor Consultation offer was available at the time of placing the order.   For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.   Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!     Regards,  Shruti Vaviya
notes.body_html:

As per telephonic conversation, For the Free Doctor Consultation offer after completing your order. We are happy to guide you on how to avail this benefit:

Visit the “My Orders” section in your account.

Locate the relevant order and click on the Free Doctor Consultation option.

A coupen code will be displayed on the screen.

Use Coupen code to proceed further and select your preferred doctor, along with the date and time for the consultation.

Once you have selected the date and time, click on “Place Order”. Your consultation will then be scheduled without any payment.

Please note: This option will only be visible for orders where the Free Doctor Consultation offer was available at the time of placing the order.


For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section. 

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Have a great day ahead!

Regards,
Shruti Vaviya
